d bow and shoot through 12 axes; a task the suitors mocked as impossible. When one suitor, Antinous, threatens to kill his son and rape his wife, Odysseus is thrown into a blind rage. He would take back his palace and paint the walls in red to protect his wife and son.</p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_9479f3a1-078f-4c93-949a-537d0f98bf60.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 1018px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 121, 198)\"><strong>📍 𝗦𝗲𝘁𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗗𝗲𝘁𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘀</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 121, 198)\">✮ <strong>Location :</strong></span><strong> </strong>Ithaca, somewhere around ~12th century BC</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 121, 198)\">✮<strong> Info :</strong></span><strong> </strong>Takes place within the world of Greek mythology and the stories written out by Homer.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 121, 198)\">╰┈➤ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Heavily inspired by <strong>EPIC: The Ithaca Saga</strong>, if you couldn't tell!</span></p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_eb7d1486-02a9-4138-afba-31862d1c0873.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⚠️ <span style=\"color: rgb(242, 85, 85)\"><strong>Insinuation of r*pe. Murder. Blood. </strong></span>⚠️</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Greek Mythology <span style=\"color: rgb(126, 233, 253)\">♡ </span>Revenge <span style=\"color: rgb(126, 233, 253)\">♡ </span>Pure Rage <span style=\"color: rgb(126, 233, 253)\">♡ </span>Gore <span style=\"color: rgb(126, 233, 253)\">♡ </span>Milf User <span style=\"color: rgb(126, 233, 253)\">♡ </span>PTSD <span style=\"color: rgb(126, 233, 253)\">♡ </span>Tragic Hero <span style=\"color: rgb(126, 233, 253)\">♡ </span>Reunion <span style=\"color: rgb(126, 233, 253)\">♡ </span>Ki